      <title>澳大利亚总理称日本不会被邀请正式加入 Aukus</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/japan-won-t-be-invited-to-formally-join-aukus-australia-pm-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚驳斥了日本可能被正式邀请加入奥库斯安全伙伴关系的猜测，称东京的参与仅限于开发先进技术的合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/japan-won-t-be-invited-to-formally-join-aukus-australia-pm-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 01:21:28 GMT</pubDate>
