    <item>
      <title>特朗普检察官敦促最高法院允许 1 月 6 日快速审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/trump-prosecutor-urges-supreme-court-to-allow-quick-jan-6-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特别检察官杰克·史密斯 (Jack Smith) 敦促美国最高法院允许对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 进行刑事审判，罪名是试图推翻他 2020 年大选的失败，因为检察官在 11 月总统投票前夕的日程上争分夺秒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/trump-prosecutor-urges-supreme-court-to-allow-quick-jan-6-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 23:51:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本岸田将寻求避免与拜登的团结分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/japan-s-kishida-will-look-to-sidestep-cracks-in-unity-with-biden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄前往华盛顿，寻求加强日本与美国的联盟，同时回避对两国关系不利的问题——包括计划收购美国钢铁公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/japan-s-kishida-will-look-to-sidestep-cracks-in-unity-with-biden</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 23:45:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员敦促美国重新对委内瑞拉马杜罗实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/senators-urge-us-to-reimpose-sanctions-on-venezuela-s-maduro</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国两党参议员团体敦促总统乔·拜登惩罚委内瑞拉总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗，因为他攻击了他的主要反对派竞争对手，称即将举行的选举未能兑现自由和公平投票的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/senators-urge-us-to-reimpose-sanctions-on-venezuela-s-maduro</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 22:03:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>厄瓜多尔前副总统可能很快重返监狱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/ecuador-s-jailed-ex-vice-president-in-coma-after-taking-pills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[厄瓜多尔监狱部门周一表示，几天前被强行从墨西哥大使馆带走的厄瓜多尔前副总统豪尔赫·格拉斯目前正在瓜亚基尔海军医院接受观察，预计将在数小时内返回牢房。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/ecuador-s-jailed-ex-vice-president-in-coma-after-taking-pills</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 21:37:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国、英国、澳大利亚考虑将日本加入对抗中国的协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/us-uk-and-australia-weigh-adding-japan-to-pact-to-counter-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高级官员周一表示，美国、英国和澳大利亚可能会将日本纳入其旗舰防务条约，就在日本首相访问华盛顿的几天前，随着中国增强军事野心，三国希望建立统一战线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/us-uk-and-australia-weigh-adding-japan-to-pact-to-counter-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 17:38:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国在推动行业发展方面利益攸关，不应该听取耶伦的意见</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/china-has-too-much-at-stake-in-industry-push-to-listen-to-yellen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[珍妮特·耶伦最近几天在中国得到了受人尊敬的听证会，她的主要信息是——北京的制造业驱动力对其他经济体构成威胁。但她的热情接待可能不会转化为她想要的政策转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/china-has-too-much-at-stake-in-industry-push-to-listen-to-yellen</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 13:40:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列官员对与哈马斯的停火谈判表示乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/israel-officials-optimistic-over-talks-with-hamas-on-gaza-hostages-cease-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列高级官员表示，加沙停火谈判已取得进展，其中包括释放人质和巴勒斯坦囚犯，此举引起了极右翼部长的批评，他们威胁要推翻政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/israel-officials-optimistic-over-talks-with-hamas-on-gaza-hostages-cease-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 11:49:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦威胁对援助俄罗斯战争的中国银行实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/yellen-threatens-sanctions-for-china-banks-that-aid-russia-s-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦结束了在中国为期四天的会谈，并警告不要采取任何增强俄罗斯军事能力的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-08/yellen-threatens-sanctions-for-china-banks-that-aid-russia-s-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2024 06:33:35 GMT</pubDate>
